---------------------------------------

### New concept- Defer
Defers the execution of that function untill surrounding function finish. concecutive defer statements will be stacked up. Last-in-first-out

func main()
{
  defer fmt.Println("World")
  fmt.Println("Hello")
}

>>>> Hello
World
